aq´anal. N-chi b´aj t-ximan qa a Hagrid b´i´n nim ti´chaq kyi´j unicornios tze´nku b´i´n ti´j kyi´j txuk, extzun b´a´n t-xilen qa otaq tz´el tniky´ ti´j
aju mya b´a´n ky-q´ob´ ky-q´ob´ n-chi b´isun.
Toj q´ij ja´lin otaq b´ant tu´n t-xi ttzyu´n kab´e tal t-xu´jil unicornio. Mya ikyjo
unicornios ma che chʼiy, puro qʼan pwaq qe. Parvati extzen Lavanda
n-chi b´et toj junjen b´e te tzalajb´il tej t-xi tka´yin kye, extzen a Pansy
