“Oh mya tajb´en jlu,” chi Hermione, n-ok t-xmoxin Weird Wizarding Dilemmas. «Alkye twitz txʼotxʼ taj tuʼn tkubʼ tbʼinchaʼn ttzmal ttziʼ
