Xi t-xo´n Winky juntl majl, n-chi tka´yin twitz Harry.
“Master — hic — yab´?”
A t-tzi´ t-xe tzaj tzyet tu´n t-xupin.
“Pero mya b´i´n qu´n qa ax tok,” chi Hermione jun rat.
¡Aju xnaq´tzal tajb´en te — hic — Winky! tzaj t-xob´il elf.
